== Ubuzima ==
Aquereburu yavukiye muri [[Togo]] umubyeyi ukomoka muri [[Gwadelupe|Guadeloupe]]<ref>Togo/ Who is Angela Aquereburu? - Myafricainfos <nowiki>https://myafricainfos.com</nowiki> › togo-who-...</ref> . Ashishikajwe n'ubuhanzi kuva akiri muto, yize muri Togo na Pointe-a-Pitre, Guadeloupe mbere yo kwimukira i Paris kwiga mu ishuri ry'ubucuruzi rya ESCP <ref>Angela Aquereburu - Serieseries.tv <nowiki>https://www.serieseries.tv</nowiki> › content › angela-aquerebur...</ref>.  Yabonye impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga mu kwihangira imirimo.  Aquereburu yashakanye n'umukinnyi wa filime Jean-Luc Rabatel kandi akora mu bakozi imyaka myinshi<ref>Angela Aquereburu - Fiche Personne sur Africultures <nowiki>http://africultures.com</nowiki> › php</ref>. Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubwo yari mu biruhuko muri Togo, yamenye ko kuri televiziyo hari amakinamico gusa, maze afatanije n’umugabo we bazana igitekerezo cyo gukurikiranya filimi yitwa motorcycle taxis.<ref>Interview with Angela Aquereburu, Director of the ... <nowiki>https://adweknow.com</nowiki> › interview-year...</ref>  Umwaka ukurikira, Aquereburu na Rabatel bimukiye i Lomé maze bashinga isosiyete ikora amajwi n'amashusho Yobo Studios<ref>Angela AQUEREBURU (YoBo Studios) - Viadeo <nowiki>https://viadeo.journaldunet.com</nowiki> › year...</ref>.  Igitekerezo cyabo cyo kwerekana tagisi cyashingiweho kuri ''Zem'', mini-serie ya episode 26 yiminota itanu, ifatanije na Canal + Afrique.<ref>Angela Aquereburu, la Shonda Rhimes togolaise - Jeune ... <nowiki>https://www.jeuneafrique.com</nowiki> › culture</ref> 

Umushinga we ukurikira wari urukurikirane rugufi  rwa filimi ya ''Palabres''<ref>African kindergartens - What language to speak at home? <nowiki>http://www.tv5monde.com</nowiki> › progra...</ref> .  Muri 2017, yatangije ''ibitaro IT'', bikemura ibibazo byabaturage nka malariya no kwera uruhu kandi byibanda ku mico Idriss na Tania<ref>Angela Aquereburu - Télérama.fr <nowiki>https://www.telerama.fr</nowiki> › personality</ref>. Aquereburu yavuze ko yatewe inkunga n'inda ye ya kabiri yo gukora iki gitaramo. Grey's Anatomy yagize uruhare runini.  Yatsindiye igihembo cy'uruhererekane rwiza mu iserukiramuco rya Vues d'Afrique i Montreal<ref>Angela Aquereburu Archives - The New Reporter <nowiki>https://www.lenouveaureporter.com</nowiki> › ...</ref>. 

